#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:4
msgid ":index:`Setting the Cover Art <cover art; setting>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:8
msgid ""
"Depending on the option settings, you can change or confirm the cover art to "
"save with a track or album."
msgstr ""
"Dependendo da opção configurada, você pode mudar ou confirmar a capa antes "
"de salvá-la com a trilha ou álbum."

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:10
msgid ""
"Once the release information has been downloaded, selecting an album or "
"track in the right-hand pane will display both the original and new coverart "
"for the selected item. You can easily replace the coverart image used for "
"the selected item by dragging the image from the file browser and dropping "
"it on the New Cover Art image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:25
msgid ""
"By right clicking on the image and selecting :menuselection:`\"Choose local "
"file…\"` from the menu, you can choose a local file as the cover art."
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:27
msgid "The context menu also provides several additional options:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:29
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Show more details…` opens the cover art information window "
"showing detailed information about the selected artwork."
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:30
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Keep original cover art` restores the original artwork if "
"new cover art has been downloaded or added."
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:31
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Choose local file…` allows selecting one or more image files "
"from the local filesystem to use as cover art."
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:32
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Add from URL…` downloads an image from a specified URL and "
"adds it as cover art."
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:34
msgid ""
"The menu also includes options controlling how newly added images are "
"handled:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:36
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Replace front cover art` replaces the existing front cover "
"image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:37
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Append front cover art` adds the new image while keeping the "
"existing artwork."
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:39
msgid ""
"Selecting :menuselection:`\"Show more details\"` will bring up a new window "
"as:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/coverart.rst:54
msgid ""
"Double-clicking an image will open the image file in the system default "
"program for the image type."
msgstr ""
